{"tid":2268890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"泰國政府ban咗pronhub","createTime":"2020-11-03T06:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T07:11:11.000Z","uid":211994,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e99950df8b495348f29d042cf93a2d299c3067","tid":2268890,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"<em><span class=\"small\">樓主知道好多連登仔覺得加山好垃圾，無奈我搵唔到其他香港嘅報道，如果有麻煩貼出嚟</span></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有泰國網民發現於星期一晚上（2號）及星期二早上（3號）均無法進入著名成人網站Pornhub，當嘗試載入網頁時頁面上會出現「相關內容已被禁止」的字眼。<br />\n<br />\n有網民猜測此舉是針對早前有示威者於Pornhub刊登廣告宣傳示威運動一事，事件令「泰國社運」短暫成為Pornhub搜尋器的搜索第一位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dbchannel.hk/2020/11/03/【與雄為敵】hey-guys-泰國have-a-ban-for-you-實施禁令ban-pornhub/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbchannel.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F03%2F%E3%80%90%E8%88%87%E9%9B%84%E7%82%BA%E6%95%B5%E3%80%91hey-guys-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8Bhave-a-ban-for-you-%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4ban-pornhub%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0ElgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=74028d83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dbchannel.hk/2020/11/03/【與雄為敵】hey-guys-泰國have-a-ban-for-you-實施禁令ban-pornhub/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">Twitter要人！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0LtTN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0LtTN9.png&h=d2e116f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e780f6ea87984b11a66d98c70626356db04b3882","tid":2268890,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4443852271942d66332a329a049d0d6b2cd41b","tid":2268890,"uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"據了解，製作鏗鏘集721特輯的港台節目製作人員工會主席蔡玉玲被警方上門拘捕，目前未知